metadata.name: Wrapped Hotels #1
metadata.description:
"First came the need for food, second came shelter"

    Wrapped Hotels is a collection of 10.000 unique hotel rooms divided
    into 3 categories, each with a specific function: rooms, lounges and
    reception desks.
    
    A Wrapped Hotels NFT acts as a deed of ownership for its equivalent
    room in The Sandbox metaverse. Thus, the owner of a Wrapped Hotels
    NFT also has ownership rights to the Sandbox equivalent.
